<title>Copy a Map</title>
<context HID_EDIT_COPY />

Click <image copy_button.png /> on the toolbar or click the <b>Edit</b> menu and then click <b>Copy</b>.

<subheader>Tips</subheader>

<list>
	<li>You can paste the map into most word processors.</li>
	<li>You can paste the map into most drawing programs, such as Paintbrush.</li>
	<li>You can also use <b>Ctrl+C</b> to copy the map to the clipboard.</li>
</list>
